summary: 21 'Game Of Thrones' Characters Who Will DEFINITELY Die In Season 8
title: 21 'Game Of Thrones' Characters Who Will DEFINITELY Die In Season 8
excerpt: While there are many months left to go until Game of Thrones Season 8, it's never to early to think about the final season. Whether you're deep in the middle of a series-long re-watch or just feeling some kind of pop culture homesickness for the…
description:
These are some good guesses but I doubt that Arya Stark will actually die. I read somewhere that George RR Martin promised his wife that Arya would survive. The original outline of the books suggests that Arya having spent the books seeking vengeance loses her taste for it. Then again it suggests that she marries Jon which will not happen.

Jaime Lannister and Cercei are doomed however as is Euron Greyjoy, Gregor Clegane and Melisandre. Perhaps Theon Greyjoy as well. 

I am on the fence about Daenerys Targaryen and Jon Snow since one or both may die.

summary: What are your unpopular ASOIAF opinions ?
question: What are your unpopular ASOIAF opinions ?
answer:
I think all of my opinions are unpopular especially on tumblr but well grounded :)

Consider these :

Arya won’t marry Gendry, it has always been one-sided with these two. Gendry will never be a king.

Rhaegar loved Lyanna. Lyanna chose to go with him. They were probably married. 

Daenerys is not the mad queen. Jon will not betray her.

The Faceless Men were behind Joffrey’s death. Oberyn poisoned Tywin.


Thank you for the question :)
